file=Executive Office/echo/marketplace/investor-update-generator/assets/investor_update_template.md · [n—:[Company Name] — [Month YYYY] Investor Update=**Sent by:** [your name]\n**Sent on:** [YYYY-MM-DD]\n**Recipients:** [number] (investors + [advisors / extended network])\n\n · t:TL;DR=[3 lines — top win, top lowlight, top ask]\n\n · h:Highlights=- [Specific win with number / context]\n- [Specific win with number / context]\n- [Specific win with number / context]\n · l/r:Lowlights / risks=- [What missed, why, what we're doing about it]\n- [What's at risk, our current view]\n\n · tb=\| Metric \| This month \| Last month \| Δ \| · tb=\|--------\|------------\|------------\|---\| · tb=\| [MRR / ARR] \| $[X] \| $[Y] \| [+%] \| · tb=\| [Growth rate (MoM)] \| [%] \| [%] \| [...] \| · tb=\| [Customers / logos] \| [N] \| [N-1] \| [+] \| · tb=\| [Key product metric] \| [value] \| [value] \| [...] \| · tb=\| [Cash] \| $[X] \| $[Y] \| [...] \| · tb=\| **Runway (months)** \| [N] \| [N+1] \| [...] \| · m:Metrics=[1-3 sentences of context: why metrics moved as they did]\n\n · p:Product=- **Shipped:** [1-3 things shipped this month, with impact]\n- **Coming next month:** [1-2 things in flight]\n- **Decisions ahead:** [any roadmap decisions you're weighing]\n\n · s/g:Sales / GTM=- **New logos:** [count and / or names if shareable]\n- **Pipeline:** [shape of pipeline — coverage, key opps]\n- **Churn / contraction:** [if relevant]\n- **Notable wins / losses:** [1-2]\n\n · t:Team=- **New hires:** [name(s), role(s), start date]\n- **Departures:** [name(s), role(s), context if relevant]\n- **Open roles:** [list — see asks below for hiring intros]\n\n · a:Asks=Specific things you can help with:\n\n1. **[Hiring]:** Intros to [specific role profile, e.g., "Senior backend engineers in NYC who've shipped billing systems"]\n2. **[Customers]:** Intros to [specific buyer profile, e.g., "Heads of Operations at SaaS companies 200-1000 employees"]\n3. **[Advisors / expertise]:** [Anyone with experience in / domain expertise around X]\n4. **[Other]:** [Anything else specific]\n\nIf you're not sure how you can help with the above, no need to respond — we'll loop you in if something specific comes up.\n\n · la:Looking ahead=- **Next milestone we're targeting:** [...]\n- **Next 3 months focus:** [...]\n- **Decisions coming up:** [...]\n\n\n*Reply to this email with thoughts, questions, or any of the asks above. Thanks for being on the journey.*\n\n— [Founder name]\n